=== Commercial and cultural ===
George Armour was a pioneer in many ways. Many of the tasks he and close colleagues initiated and became involved with continue to exist and have repercussions to this day.

==== Usurpation of good deeds by the meatpackers ====
Very frequently George Armour has been taken to be a brother or relative of [[Philip Danforth Armour]].

Examples of web sites and books that erroneously indicate that George Armour was closely related to Philip Danforth Armour include the following:
* {{ URL | http://cootershistorything.blogspot.com/2014/08/armour-dole-company-of-chicago.html }}
* {{ URL | http://articles.chicagotribune.com/1994-08-31/business/9408310113_1_merchants-savings-grand-banking-hall-lasalle-street }}
